import React, { useState } from 'react' import { useDispatch } from 'react-redux' import { setLogged } from './slices/logSlice' export default function Login() { const dispatch = useDispatch() const [userType, setUserType] = useState(0) const handleSubmit = (e) =>{ e.preventDefault(); dispatch(setLogged(true)) dispatch(setUserType(userType)) } return (

{ (userType === 0) ? 'Login Cliente' : 'Login Entregador'}
